de.renew.net.arc

Class RollbackArcExecutable

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.renew.net.arc.RollbackArcExecutable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.renew.engine.searcher.Executable, de.renew.engine.searcher.LateExecutable

    public class RollbackArcExecutable
extends java.lang.Object
    The rollback arc's executable. Moves the token through the rollback arc from the transition to the place.
    Author:
    Anton Rigin, National Research University - Higher School of Economics, Faculty of Computer Science, Master Degree Program "System and Software Engineering", the 1st year student. Term Project (Coursework) on the Topic "Reference and Data Semantic-Based Simulator of Petri Nets Extension with the Use of Renew Tool". HSE University, Moscow, Russia, 2019 - 2020.
